@node "Intr" "Introduction"
Allows you to display other doors available to users -  shit  you
couldn't  fit  on  your main menu cos there's a ton of ansi there
at bursting point.

Anyway,  there  is  one config file which holds all data for this
door, a smart door, that shows the user other commands  avail  at
his access level. Nothing else.

A  door  like  this  exists  out there, which I haven't got, so I
wrote this to compensate. Respect to  the  guy  that  wrote  that
door. MoOpen born because of you.
@endnode
